    <div class="tn-note">
      <strong>&#x1f4dd; Cultural Note:</strong> As the use of the verb translated as **cut off** in 16:17 and 18:16 indicates, the author means that Nebuchadnezzar had his men cut the **gold** off of these **furnishings**. It may be helpful to clarify this for your readers. Alternate translation: [and he cut the gold off all of the furnishings]
